Package: betRBall
Title: Tools for Football Analytics and Betting Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("William", "Wiik", email = "william.wiik@hotmail.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of tools for modeling, simulating and analyzing football matches and betting markets. 
    Includes functions for expected goals, team strength estimation, and value bet detection.
